title: Planet of the Apes - Cataclysm (001 - 012) (complete) (- Nem -)
description: Beginning in September 2012, Planet of the Apes: Cataclysm took over as BOOM!'s regular monthly series. Set eight years prior to the original Planet of the Apes, this new series is written by Corinna Sara Bechko and Gabriel Hardman, authors of both the Betrayal and Exile miniseries, and mixes several characters from those series with characters from the original movie.
